---
title: Caribbean Coconut Jackfruit with Garlic Rice & Tomato Salsa
description: Jackfruit marinated in saucy BBQ flavouring – our favourite (and totally irresistible) veggie alternative to
pulled pork. Pair it with creamy coconut milk and Caribbean-style spices, plus a tried-and-true garlic rice for
endless deliciousness!
